strings: <voice_0x01001C9D><se_high>Media princess: We haven't been here for a long time.
<voice_0x01001C9E><se_high>Media princess: <hero> Thanks for your efforts to break the curse!
<voice_0x01001C9F><se_high>Media princess: How can I quit smoking?
<voice_0x01001CA0><se_high>Media princess: I want you to know... If you choose not to go, I will understand.
<voice_0x01001CA1><se_high>Media princess: - Why are you saying that? My father asked me a few days ago.
<voice_0x01001CA2><se_high>Media princess: He said<:> "You have your own life. It's not fair to drag him through life.
<voice_0x01001CA3><se_high>Media princess: You are doing a lot for us. I promise I will never misunderstand you. decides to continue on his own path.
